      "writtenOn": "2018-06-19T13:12:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Addressed.\n\nI had to add context buffer here, as PTRACE_GETREGSET considers register size to be 32 bits wide on 32bit mips cpu, but PTRACE_GETREGS considers all registers 64 bits wide, regardless of mips cpu bitness.",
